run-gcc (0.1.1) UNRELEASED; urgency=medium

  * Enhance compiler automation by detecting the source file extension using shell string manipulation.
    - For .c files, use gcc -std=c11.
    - For .cpp/.cc files, use g++ -std=c++2b.
    This update streamlines the workflow and reduces user errors.

